net.dnddev.factions.spatial

Interface BoundedArea

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<BoundedArea>, HyperRect<BoundedArea>

    public interface BoundedArea
extends HyperRect<BoundedArea>, Comparable<BoundedArea>
    An area that is bounded by two points. The HyperRect is part of a system called an R-Tree which is a type of spatial data structure to quickly and easily search for regions and points in a three-dimensional world.
    Author:
    Michael Ziluck
